Q: 飞机注册号为N404TC的飞机是哪一家公司的？
SQL: SELECT sd.supplier_name FROM aircraft_details ad JOIN supplier_details sd ON ad.supplier_id = sd.supplier_id WHERE ad.registration = "N404TC";
